survey_response.review_text: Oh my lucky God ! This is what my experience was. Dr Bala Guhan was such an awesome person at the first place. I am a person who was highly tensed and extremely scared about this entire process. I never expected that the doctor would make it so easy and completely painless experience for me. The way he explained me about what are the tools that he will be using, how it will make me feel and what he is gonna do next and all made me take it up with ease. Trust me, I didn't even know that my minor surgery was over untill he told me. He made me so comfortable that in between he was asking me how I was feeling. Nevertheless he is such an amazing doctor I have ever encountered in my whole life. I'm a person who is afraid even for tablets, but now I can say with confidence that I will even undergo any treatment or surgery with this doctor. A salute to Dr Bala Guhan ! My name is Prathibha !
